metadata.name: NAYUTA: 東京電脳R
metadata.description:
This is the story of NAYUTA in a Tokyo of the Future. This is the story of how she navigates three distinct belief systems.

The worldbuilding of NAYUTA: Tokyo Dennou R begins with a collection of 6,000 characters. Join us as we shape the future of Nayuta through a new form of storytelling. 

From Tokyo to the World. Art By SteakNinjaBoy.
